    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in extraordinary, mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep luster, free of any chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and a scent that still feels new. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands the highest standard of quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
